Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on May 21,2026, the following bill was signed into law:
H.B. NO. 2310, H.D. 1, S.D. 1, MAKING AN EMERGENCY APPROPRIATION TO
C.D. 1 THE DEPARTMENT OF HUMAN SERVICES.
